%% Diagram: Client OT state machine
%% Type: state
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Synchronized

    Synchronized --> AwaitingAck: local edit\n(send op, mark pending)
    AwaitingAck --> Synchronized: server ack\n(no buffered ops)

    AwaitingAck --> AwaitingWithBuffer: local edit\n(start buffer)
    AwaitingWithBuffer --> AwaitingWithBuffer: local edit\n(compose into buffer)

    AwaitingWithBuffer --> AwaitingAck: server ack\n(send buffer)

    Synchronized --> Synchronized: remote op\n(apply directly)
    AwaitingAck --> AwaitingAck: remote op\n(transform pending)
    AwaitingWithBuffer --> AwaitingWithBuffer: remote op\n(transform pending and buffer)
